Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我叫南茜  南茜·维勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, um, I'm Nancy. Nancy Wheeler.
